Prize pickup information is provided at the time of winning, for additional information please email: DavidMartinez@iheartmedia.com. In order to claim a prize, you will be required to present a copy of your drivers license or other government issued photo ID. In addition, you will be required to fill out a W9 tax form before claiming your prize.
